Example code:
```php
Code example

<?php

trait Foo 
{
    public function foo(): void {} 
}


class ParentClass 
{
    public int $a;
    
    public function bar(): void {}
}

class ChildClass extends ParentClass
{
    use Foo;
    
    public int $b;
    
    public function fooBar(): void {}
}
```

